  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>As part of the requirements for casting this jutsu you must have <strong>Rasengan</strong> on your jutsu known list. You conjure a mass of chakra with two fingers and then condense it into an inch wide swirling sphere of pure chakra and you fire it at creature you can see within range. The target creature cannot take reactions until the conclusion of this jutsu.</p><p>Make a ranged ninjutsu attack. On a hit, the target takes 8d8 Force damage and must make a Strength saving throw. On a failed save they are knocked back 30 feet and gain the dazed condition until the end of their next turn. This jutsu ignores half and three quarters cover.</p><p><strong>At Higher Ranks:</strong> For each rank you cast this jutsu above <br />A-Rank, increase the cost of this jutsu by 3 and increase the damage by 3d8.</p>",
